solutions.content:
**Idea**
- Same with problem [122. Best Time to Buy and Sell Stock II](https://leetcode.com/problems/best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock-ii/discuss/259375) except if we sell on `i`th day, we only can buy on `i+2`th day (skip `i+1`th day).
```python
class Solution:
    def maxProfit(self, prices: List[int]) -> int:
        @lru_cache(None)
        def dp(i, canBuy):
            if i >= len(prices):
                return 0
            ans = dp(i+1, canBuy)  # Skip
            if canBuy:
                ans = max(ans, dp(i+1, False) - prices[i])  # Buy
            else:
                ans = max(ans, dp(i+2, True) + prices[i])  # Sell
            return ans

        return dp(0, True)
```
Complexity:
- Time: `O(N)`
- Space: `O(N)`

