Effectively a translation of Case V in https://leetcode.com/problems/best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock-with-transaction-fee/discuss/108870/most-consistent-ways-of-dealing-with-the-series-of-stock-problems

```
class Solution:
    def maxProfit(self, prices: List[int]) -> int:
        prev_cash, cash, hold = 0, 0, float('-inf')
        for i in range(len(prices)):
            prev_cash, cash, hold = cash, max(cash, hold + prices[i]), max(hold, prev_cash - prices[i])
        return cash
```

