# Intuition
Define buy[i] as the max profit when you buy the stock at day i. sell[i] as the max profit when you sell the stock at day i. Therefore set buy[0] = -prices[0], that if you buy the stock at first day, the profit is -prices[0], also set sell[0] = 0


