**Idea:**:
* Build adjacency list
* Prune leaves until there are only 1 or 2 nodes left
* Use Kahn's Algorithm used in [LC 207. Course Schedule](https://leetcode.com/problems/course-schedule/discuss/347690/Java-or-Topological-Sort-Template-or-BFS-Kahn's-Algo-or-DFS)
**T/S:** O(n)/O(n)
